## Shader Customization

The original component used a **blue/green aurora** palette. It was recolored to the **Singular Cosmic-Tech** identity:

| Channel | Original (Aurora) | Singular (Adapted) |
|---------|-------------------|---------------------|
| Red | `0.1 + 0.3 * sin(...)` | `0.9 + 0.1 * sin(...)` |
| Green | `0.3 + 0.5 * cos(...)` | `0.3 + 0.2 * cos(...)` |
| Blue | `0.7 + 0.3 * sin(...)` | `0.02 + 0.05 * sin(...)` |

This produces warm amber/copper/orange light trails on a pure black void.

## Browser Verification ✅

- **Shader renders** — animated orange/amber light trails flowing across the hero section
- **Content readable** — hero title, subtitle, CTAs, and stats all clearly visible on top
- **No console errors** — no WebGL issues, no React errors
- **Responsive** — shader resizes with the window

